<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh nih nem tein an auh lengmang, Nihin an auh, nihin an auh, Lu-nun
 dawtnak lam zeica'h nan duh lo? Hlat hlah law, hlat hin hlah u.

[C1]
   Nihin an auh, (Nihin an auh, nihin an auh), Ni-hin an auh, (Nihin an
   auh, nihin an auh), Jesuh an auh ko, (Jesuh an auh ko, Jesuh an auh ko),
   Jesuh nih nem te-in an auh.

[V2]
 Re-thei-mi dinh duh ah Jesuh a au, Nihin a au, nihin a au, Amah sinah
 nan thil ritmi thum u, Nannih an hlaw hna lai lo.

[C2]
   Nihin an auh, (Nihin an auh, nihin an auh), Ni-hin an auh, (Nihin an
   auh, nihin an auh), Jesuh an auh ko, (Jesuh an auh ko, Jesuh an auh ko),
   Jesuh nih nem te-in an auh.

[V3]
 Jesuh an hngah lioah atu ra u, Ni-hin an hngah, nihin an hngah, Amah
 kehram ah nan sualnak phuang u, Hngak hlah u atu ra u.

[C3]
   Nihin an auh, (Nihin an auh, nihin an auh), Ni-hin an auh, (Nihin an
   auh, nihin an auh), Jesuh an auh ko, (Jesuh an auh ko, Jesuh an auh ko),
   Jesuh nih nem te-in an auh.

[V4]
 Jesuh dawtnak bia thawng atu ngai u, Ni-hin ngai u, nihin ngai u, A
 min a zummi kha an i lawm lai, Hngak hlah u, atu ngai u.

[C4]
   Nihin an auh, (Nihin an auh, nihin an auh), Ni-hin an auh, (Nihin an
   auh, nihin an auh), Jesuh an auh ko, (Jesuh an auh ko, Jesuh an auh ko),
   Jesuh nih nem te-in an auh.</lyrics>
<title>JESUH NIH AN AUH CH237</title>
<hymn_number>237</hymn_number>
</song>